36
00:03:55,568 --> 00:03:56,796
Ucuti, Dejv.

37
00:03:57,604 --> 00:03:59,868
U Njumanu se svake nedelje
pojavljuje svetleca lopta

38
00:04:00,506 --> 00:04:02,633
